{"tid":842234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個仆街家姐真係好慘","createTime":"2018-09-30T06:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T12:01:26.000Z","uid":211074,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"56cd2dfc6c99a3ecd4326a8c1c225d185c7aa11a","tid":842234,"uid":211074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣個家姐都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong> 1.極度懶惰</strong><br />\n從來唔會做家務 洗隻碗到懶 佢間房啲碗食完幾日都唔攞出黎洗 成浸臭味 間房臭到怨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從來唔掃地唔拖地 成個地板都係塵佢都唔會理 垃圾桶滿左都唔攞出去揼 <br />\n<strong>2.冇手尾</strong><br />\n開咗燈唔會熄返燈 成個廳啲燈俾佢開曬 入返間房開足成日都無人 電費貴到仆街 水機啲水冇晒俾佢浸晒又唔識得補番啲水 搞到全家人成日飲水都要重新煲過<br />\n<strong>3.冇責任心</strong><br />\n隻狗佢買返嚟完全無理過 成個月唔帶佢出街都覺得冇問題 從來唔喂狗 唔帶隻狗出街 叫佢帶隻狗出去散下步 佢調返轉頭屌鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong>4.脾氣極臭</strong><br />\n成個公主咁唔話得 同佢講幾句嘢佢都唔耐煩 已經想爆鳩你咁滯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上述佢唔做嘅嘢全部我一覽包曬 仲有更多不能盡錄人哋啲家姐咁好 點解上天要俾個咁嘅家姐我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957b5a6b10f5ce21aa13252dee30b6d0c37925e5","tid":842234,"uid":127929,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:54:45.000Z","msg":"交比我教下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2ff357014c3ac5bec1e1ed71ee025433294995","tid":842234,"uid":210524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"想做你姐夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"